metadata.name: The way we feel
metadata.description:
I love you...
I hate you...
Thank you...
I'm sorry...
I need you...
We're saying these things and we bare our hearts to others. Sometimes we reveal more than than we want to. What others see? Are we ready for what we're about to get? Whatever it is, it's a two-way process. Some must learn to respect, and others - to accept.
Handmade digital drawing. The line pattern is made of one continuous line that never breaks and intersect.
5600x5600px
